data.meta_description: Sareyn Sareyn a small town 25 km south of Ardabil. This city is famous because of the many hot springs and a tourism areas in the province of Ardebil. City Sareyn in 04/48 and 09/38 degrees north latitude eastern longitude, with an area of 1280000 square meters is located 28 kilometers West of the city of Ardabil. The average height of 1650 meters above sea level.
